ActCanadian Tourism Commission Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of LORNE BROWNSEY of Victoria (British Columbia), as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission, representing the region set out in subparagraph 11(3)(a)(vi) of the Act, to hold office during pleasure on a part-time basis for a term of four years.
